Highly Needed for lots of high end encounters, spell is pretty rare, and Paladins arnt usually the first one to get it, Generally (Yes some guilds may do it differently) Druid &gt; Shm &gt; Paladin &gt; Cleric for order.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Stuns </b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
