<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Divine Stun </b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Lots of AA points, most things 55+ are just tagged stun immune anyways, and can shut down most CHer's without spell by nuking or moving them, bad refresh time, so if you find a target it works on, you stun it once, then it can cast again. Still a useful skill, But I didnt see you put rampage on warrior advantages: P<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> 90% Res </b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Nice For soloing/small groups, minorly important on raids if wipeout or you need to quickly get somene back in fight. Clerics got 96% thou.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Roots</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Roots Own, Not gunna argue with you there.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Divine Aura</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Not Gunna argue with ya there, DA owns<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Group Heals</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
