<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Heals</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Superior Heal is too slow, and not enuff, its decent with fast cast, but its only moderatly useful on raids. CC is good for keeping up casters, unfortunatly its lowest on HoT, and is always overwrriten. There is a new Cleric spell on test that can overwrite this, potentially lessening the use of it, but hell thats not live, thats not a present advtanage/disadvantage (More on this later)<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Slay Undead ( Damage that can hit 6k on a hit )</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
