Slay is definatly nice, but as many has mentioned there are few places that its useful, VS, IV, Rhag 1,2,3. Few nice places for soloing, but not an abondance, and its not really too much of an increase over FG XP rate.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Dispells</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Nice, but lot of other class's have this, Not too useful<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Cures</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
