<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Anti Undead Spells</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
The ratio on these is so outdated, the DPS Increase from using these is minimal due to lost melee DPS (And since your fighting undead, thats less time for IoN or Slay to proc)<br>
