About Jan, this year started a warrior because I wanted to be viable in the endgame. I'm sure I read about some grumbling concerning taunt and I did look at all the melee sub-classes but decided I couldn't go wrong being a warrior. <br>
<br>
Hell, now VI starts fixing the druid class that I orginally started with and unbalances the entire melee sub class.  WTF!  I guess the answer is Ebay!   Go buy a damned Pally, since this class is working beautifully that way I can recover some of time I invested in my warrior.<br>
<br>
Who knows, maybe after EQ-3, they'll get around to fixing the warrior class in EQ-1.<br>
